hopobject.body: What do you do? high blood pressure medicine losartan side effects Birds of feather it is said. Love to see the criminals sue each other for lying to each other! Does anyone, I mean ANYONE, not know that banks today are nothing more than continuing criminal enterprises protected by the ones they own in Congress, etc.? Big banks are the bane of the world, there is no doubt. Do you need a list of their latest crimes for which there will be no meaningful punishment? Don’t you wish you could rob someone, get caught, pay a PUNY fine AND keep all the money you stole? Oh…an no jail of course. That is how banks work today. Clearly. Bank of America is a great example of crime in action.
